{"tid":993391,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"夫妻之間最大既考驗：生BB！","createTime":"2019-01-24T01:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T01:56:40.000Z","uid":196627,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c69b25d933784b4afeb9fe35e6912b453aa3d2e4","tid":993391,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:49:05.000Z","msg":"身為一個媽媽<br />\n我覺得兩公婆最大考驗一定係生BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為生完到而家<br />\n老公仲同我時不時為左BB黎嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生BB前產前檢查，產前講座，BB健康，BB將來既路等等同老公嘈<br />\n生BB之後，為左產後護理，BB奶粉，照顧BB既時間，BB既學習等等<br />\n而家甚至為左我既身形黎嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係雞毛蒜皮既野都可以嘈一餐<br />\n但如果可以經歷到呢關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相信大家既感情會更深厚<br />\n希望過到啦"},{"pid":"fd1927f141c27235c2bfbd69b95faa3d3ce3d2b3","tid":993391,"uid":44339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"BB 幾大？<br />\n為身形嘈...有點過份"},{"pid":"9466b83ed92ed2ae3c876ada16c1f39d4ea8bcf4","tid":993391,"uid":94828,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:52:36.000Z","msg":"兩個男人生到仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d38dd312dfd717b9b3a536d831ee45dac5af2e2","tid":993391,"uid":48109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd1927f141c27235c2bfbd69b95faa3d3ce3d2b3","tid":993391,"uid":44339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"BB 幾大？<br />\n為身形嘈...有點過份"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:52:53.000Z","msg":"善用起底"},{"pid":"57d48c0ed95a237f379ffb4417d21d83f3db797c","tid":993391,"uid":221813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T01:53:09.000Z","msg":"直情改變哂個人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4502c476ad6273133758d95a590d2d18bc33c53","tid":993391,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":